Scope of this dedication
------------------------
This CC0 dedication applies to the *catalog metadata* produced in this
repository: the CSV files under `data/`, the Markdown dataset cards under
`dataset_cards/`, and the templates. These files describe third-party datasets;
they do not contain, and add no new rights to, the underlying data themselves.

Each underlying dataset referenced in this catalog remains subject to its own
license and terms of use. Anyone reusing an underlying dataset must comply with
that dataset's license, not this one.

